    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 987.1 Cayman S features the mid-mounted 3.4L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and fresh bushings, maintaining the surgical turn-in these platforms are known for. Recent service includes a borescope inspection, RMS check, and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires on factory staggered alloys. This is a driver-focused example with a clean title, ready for the canyons.",
