    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for car that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seating remains firm and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s entry bolster. All electronic components, including the touchscreen navigation, dual-zone climate control, and the premium audio system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has a documented service history, with a recent oil service and brake pad replacement performed within the last 3,000 miles. The engine idles smoothly and the transmission shifts through gears without hesitation. While it shows the typical character of a pre-owned vehicle, its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal make it a reliable choice for any discerning driver.",
